{"tid":1886773,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"支持《頭條新聞》 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-02-19T06:26:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T08:33:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8c15460e8e5e432cc26f45b289445e47ecc22a12","tid":1886773,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:26:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200219/20864748/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200219%2F20864748%2F&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=2f0c1e89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200219%2F20864748%2F&h=2e2a95bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200219/20864748/</a><br />\n<br />\n支持《頭條新聞》 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200219/large/1582008892_e72a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200219%2Flarge%2F1582008892_e72a.jpg&h=6cbb6e3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《無品芝麻官》截圖<br />\n<br />\n全靠警務處處長PK鄧（由一姓郭的代行）致信廣播處長投訴港台《頭條新聞》嘲諷警隊，極度遺憾──於是大家知道這個節目有嘢睇而且好好睇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">全靠干涉編採自由之手段，各界爭相重溫，這集《無品芝麻官》點擊率飆升，網民還發起一人一信支援，及推上百萬views，力抗邪惡勢力。</span>各用各的方法，支持以嬉笑怒罵形式反映社會現象，諷刺時弊的節目，尊重港台（及所有良心傳媒）專業編輯報導自主，港人團結抗疫抗黑。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得新一季的《頭條新聞》好看，<span style=\"color: orange;\">王喜獨立的《警棍》已很生鬼，而另起《驚方訊息》也獲力撐</span>。除原班人馬曾志豪吳志森羅啟新外，還加入王宗堯，拉高顏值又有新鮮感&hellip;&hellip;期待下一集。<br />\n<br />\n也歡迎「驚慌」投訴，把遭抹黑的真相公諸於世，如何重裝備抗炎防疫，錫身過前線醫護還只顧自拍，在街坊抗議該區建隔離中心時毒打及抓捕，來「保護市民」&hellip;&hellip;警隊公開一切還自己「清白」，毋須意圖威嚇。<br />\n<br />\n在政府和黑警專注禍港殃民不封關不理有人詐騙口罩搶劫廁紙（真荒謬！）時，李嘉誠已動用全球網絡採購，捐贈口罩和防護物資繼續進行了，加上民間力量，毒娥害死港人的奸計是不會得逞的！ <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"a3ad0c14a217706da2010c74f5b08faab9ba5168","tid":1886773,"uid":265416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:32:01.000Z","msg":"李碧華一向高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b5ad625653cbd23da8716c30f0299799ecd51c","tid":1886773,"uid":244693,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:46:52.000Z","msg":"碧華姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1483b5ef7ba81b34626f906ef98c40e59bd716","tid":1886773,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:31:32.000Z","msg":"天誅地滅黑警"},{"pid":"bf605e2da67724dd9801a200c3e6bdee7920621a","tid":1886773,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:33:36.000Z","msg":"高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20cc835bde07696f8f3cf8959bd681d0a6b429b3","tid":1886773,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:33:46.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FWX2m1d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFWX2m1d.gif&h=f26d93c1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oN1VG1e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoN1VG1e.gif&h=63ee98cf&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ewbq4ey.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fewbq4ey.gif&h=cca3bdbe&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"}]}